new features
============
    * highlight the last changed variable (in the local variables tab) [Dodji seketeli]

bug fixes/improvements
======================
    * don't redraw the local variables widget at each stop [Dodji Seketeli]
    * don't assert when hover on empty space [Dodji Seketeli]
    * sync each log line to disk [Dodji Seketeli]

|||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||

Disclaimer:
============
This it the first official release, so remember that it could eat your cat or
make your landlord divorce. In any case, let us know the problems you encounter so that
we can fix them in coming releases.

Features
================================
* basic target control (stepping)
* breakpoint management
* debugging session management
* local variables inspection
* call stack management

